quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,96,Aur agar unn bastiyon kay rehney walay eman ley aatay aur perhezgari ikhtiyar kertay to hum unn per aasman aur zamin ki barkaten khol detay lekin unhon ney takzeeb ki to hum ney unn kay aemaal ki waja say unn ko pakar liya
  7,97,Kiya phir bhi inn bastiyon kay rehney walay iss baat say bey fikar ho gaye hain kay unn per humara azab shab kay waqt aa paray jiss waqt woh sotay hon
  7,98,Aur kiya inn bastiyon kay rehney walay iss baat say bey fikar hogaye hain kay inn per humara azab din charhay aa paray jiss waqt kay woh apney khelon mein masghool hon
  7,99,Kiya pus woh Allah ki iss pakar say bey fikar hogaye. So Allah ki pakar say ba-juz unn kay jin ki shamat hi aagaee ho aur koi bey fikar nahi hota
  7,100,Aur kiya unn logon ko jo zamin kay waris huye wahan kay logon ki halakat kay baad (inn waqiyaat-e-mazkoor ney) yeh baat nahi batlaee kay agar hum chahayen to inn kay jurm kay sabab inn ko halak ker dalen aur hum inn kay dilon per band laga denpus woh na sunn saken
  7,101,Inn bastiyon kay kuch kuch qissay hum aap say biyan ker rahey hain aur inn sab kay pass unn kay payghumbar mojzaat ley ker aaye phir jiss cheez ko enhon ney ibtidaa mein jhoota keh diya yeh baat nahi hui kay phir iss ko maan letay Allah Taalaa issi tarah kafiron kay dilon per band laga deta hai
  7,102,Aur aksar logon mein hum ney wafay-e-ehad na rakha aur hum ney aksar logon ko bey hukum hi paya
  7,103,Phir inn kay baad hum ney musa (alh-e-salam) ko apney dalaeel dey ker firaon aur uss kay umraa kay pass bheja magar unn logon ney inn kay bilkul haq ada na kiya. So dekhiye unn mufisdon ka kiya anjam hua
  7,104,Aur musa (alh-e-salam) ney farmaya kay aey firaon! Mein rabbul aalameen ki taraf say payghumbr hun